<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2017-11-13</DATELINE><TITLE>Gut Brain Axis and Its Microbiota Regulation in Mammals and Birds</TITLE><BODY>This article provides a brief overview of the advances made in microbiota research in parrots and pet birds. It describes this complex ecosystem and the contribution of the intestinal microbiota to host health and disease, including the nervous system.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>